# NOTE: do not blanket-ignore *.cmake here. Generated CMake files already live
# in the ignored build directories above, while vendored dependencies ship
# required modules such as third_party/fmt/support/cmake/JoinPaths.cmake and
# third_party/cpptrace/cmake/*.cmake. Ignoring them breaks every build made
# from a fresh clone (CMake: "include could not find requested file").
